# rehanmd.tech is now content-managed via git — Claude Code edits the
# repo directly. No admin auth, no LLM keys, no KV/Blob storage required.
#
# This file is intentionally minimal. Copy to .env.local if you spin up
# a local dev server; otherwise nothing needs to be set.

# Optional — only if you want a custom production URL distinct from rehanmd.tech.
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=https://rehanmd.tech
